Content: I've tried unplugging and plugging back in, but the computer still won't start. The power button lights up but nothing happens.
I'll check the hardware diagnostics and get back to you within 30 minutes.
This is urgent as I need to access the payroll system for month-end processing.
The installation completed successfully. Thank you for the quick resolution!
Great! Please let me know if you need any additional software installations.
Everything is working perfectly now. Closing this ticket.
The printer shows a paper jam error, but I don't see any paper stuck inside.

I'll need to check the Exchange server settings. This might take 1-2 hours to resolve.

Found a memory leak in the CRM module. Applied patch and restarted the application server.
Confirmed the fix is working. Application has been stable for over an hour now.
Ticket resolved and closed. Will monitor system performance over the next 24 hours.

I'll check the VPN server logs and network configuration. Please try connecting again in 30 minutes.
Still having the same issue. Connection drops every few minutes.
Getting 'Access Denied' error when trying to connect to the HR database.
File sharing is working now. Thank you for the quick resolution!
The network permissions were updated. You should have full access to the shared drives now.
Keys Q, W, and E are not responding at all. Other keys work fine.

I'll contact procurement to expedite the license renewal process.

I'll need to expand the backup storage and run a manual backup tonight.

Phone issue resolved. New handset was installed and is working perfectly.
The old phone will be recycled according to company policy.
Conference room A projector won't display laptop screen. Tried different cables.

I'll reset your OneDrive cache and reconfigure the sync settings.

I'll check the backup systems immediately. This is high priority given the timeline.

Old laptop will be refurbished and added to the spare equipment inventory.
Thank you for the quick turnaround. This really helped with my case deadlines.
